embed subtitles into video
`ffmpeg -i inputFilePath -i subtitleFilePath -c copy -c:s mov_text -map 0 -map 1 outputFilePath
`
extract subtitles from video
ffmpeg -i inputFilePath -map 0:s:0 -c:s srt outputFilePath

